Class PrepareM2MQualityBlackboardPartitionJob

java.lang.Object
  de.upb.m2m.quality.configurator.jobs.PrepareM2MQualityBlackboardPartitionJob
All Implemented Interfaces:
de.uka.ipd.sdq.workflow.IBlackboardInteractingJob<de.uka.ipd.sdq.workflow.mdsd.blackboard.MDSDBlackboard>, de.uka.ipd.sdq.workflow.IJob
public class PrepareM2MQualityBlackboardPartitionJob
extends java.lang.Object
implements de.uka.ipd.sdq.workflow.IBlackboardInteractingJob<de.uka.ipd.sdq.workflow.mdsd.blackboard.MDSDBlackboard>

Job for preparing the work flow's blackboard for a measurement of metrics for a specific language. The preparation's main task is to to set up a blackboard partition for metamodels of (1) the transformation language of interest and (2) the metrics to be measured.

Version:
0.1
Author:
Kapova et al., Sebastian Lehrig (lehrig@mail.upb.de)
